{
  "stem": "512.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] how we conduct Yom Kippur Eve in those barracks-- some of the girls, it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Where is God?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Didn't answer us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So in the morning, we went to work, and it passed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then when it came the really, late already the winter, they didn't have enough gas for the trucks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The trucks-- we would load the, the bombs on the truck and the truck would take them into a-- underground bunkers, they called them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But then they, they ran out of gas.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They didn't have any gas.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I think that was during the war for the Nazis a minus.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They didn't have enough gas, gasoline.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they took us, the girls, and we were pulling those trucks to the bunkers in the big snow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sometimes the shoe would get stuck in the big snow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we've got to work, move.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then it was stopped altogether.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't have, I guess, material, whatever.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we would, they would-- there would be a lot of air raids-- this is how we figured it, already-- a lot of air raids, almost nightly.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We would be woken up and taken into the bunkers, hidden because they were not afraid for us that we were going to perish or something, but they were afraid, you know, to put on the lights and then planes might spot it.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So sometimes they-- for that reason, they kept us in those bunkers with food and water.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one night, tragedy happened to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Somebody-- I fell asleep because we were so tired from the marching to work, marching from work, and pulling those things that my wooden shoe, somebody took it off of my foot.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was left barefoot in the morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
